snippet.title: ｈａｃｋｍｕｄ launch trailer
snippet.description:
h a c k m u d is out NOW! Buy it on humble, itch, or steam:
https://www.humblebundle.com/store/hackmud
https://drizzlybear.itch.io/hackmud
http://store.steampowered.com/app/469920

h a c k m u d is a cyberpunk themed text-based hacking simulator for intel-compatible personal home computers. Get lost in a deep and complex world full of challenging puzzles.
